      "selector": "aria_label:Why do you want to join Figma?",
      "value": "I am deeply inspired by Figma's transformative impact on creative collaboration and its dedication to building accessible, powerful design tools. My background as a Data Science student, coupled with hands-on experience in Generative AI, LLM Systems, and Machine Learning, aligns perfectly with Figma's innovative approach to empowering users, especially as AI continues to reshape design workflows.\n\nI am eager to apply my proficiency in Python, PyTorch, LangChain, and robust backend development to enhance Figma's platform. I believe my ability to build and deploy sophisticated AI-powered applications and work with complex data systems would be invaluable in advancing Figma’s mission and contributing to its future groundbreaking features.",
