      "selector": "aria_label:Additional Information",
      "value": "Beyond my academic pursuits as a Master's Data Science student at the University of Maryland (3.74 GPA), I possess hands-on experience in building and deploying AI-powered applications. My ongoing AI Intern role at Raising The Floor involves significant contributions to assistive technology and HCI research. I have a proven track record in Generative AI and LLM Systems, leveraging frameworks like LangChain, HuggingFace, and PyTorch, alongside backend expertise with FastAPI and AWS. My personal projects, including launchway.app and mimikree.com, further demonstrate my proficiency in translating complex data science concepts into practical, impactful solutions. I am eager to apply this blend of research, development, and deployment skills to your team.",
